-- MOVES-Perella Weinberg appoints Jorma Ollila as advisory partner
-- 
-- Mon Jun 30, 2014 06:48AM EDT
-- None



June 30 (Reuters) - Perella Weinberg Partners, an asset management services company,  appointed Jorma Ollila as an advisory partner.

Ollila is currently chairman of the board at Royal Dutch Shell Plc <RDSa.L> and Outokumpu Oyj <OUT1V.HE>. He was earlier chief executive officer of Nokia <NOK1V.HE>.